sentence: What is the course name for ENGR 280 ?
sentence-with-vars: What is the course name for department0 number0 ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.NAME FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "ENGR" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 280 ;
sql-with-vars: SELECT COURSEalias0.NAME FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "department0" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = number0 ;
